Date: Fri, 12 Jun 2026 10:57:31 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 1/4] Add LilyGo T-Display P4 variant (first bring-up,
 headless)

ESP32-P4 rev v1.x + XL9535-routed SX1262 control lines (ng-io-expander core)
+ overridable FS partition label for multi-firmware partition layouts.
Boots to NodeDB init under the DualMesh launcher; radio bring-up in progress.

